# Privacy Policy for Quirk - AI Personality Insights

**Last Updated:** January 3, 2026
**Effective Date:** January 3, 2026

## Introduction

Quirk ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how our Chrome extension collects, uses, and safeguards your information.

## Information We Collect

### Browsing History Data
Quirk collects the following browsing information to provide personality insights and productivity analytics:
- Website URLs you visit
- Page titles
- Visit counts and timestamps
- Time spent on websites
- Domain names (e.g., youtube.com, github.com)

### User Data
- Unique user identifier (UUID) generated locally
- Extension preferences and settings
- Chrome profile email (optional, only if you grant permission)

### Analytics Data
- Productivity scores calculated from your browsing
- AI-generated insights and personality analysis results
- Usage statistics of extension features

## How We Use Your Information

We use the collected data to:
1. **Provide Core Features:**
   - Generate daily productivity scores
   - Create AI-powered personality insights
   - Display browsing analytics and trends
   - Provide personalized roasts and motivation

2. **Improve Service:**
   - Analyze usage patterns to improve features
   - Debug and fix technical issues
   - Enhance AI analysis accuracy

3. **AI Processing:**
   - Send anonymized browsing summaries to OpenAI's GPT-4 for analysis
   - Only the top 15 most-visited sites are sent to the AI
   - No personally identifiable information is included in AI requests

## Data Storage and Security

### Where Your Data is Stored
- **Local Storage:** User preferences stored in your Chrome browser
- **Cloud Database:** Browsing data and analysis results stored securely in Supabase (PostgreSQL database)
- **Encryption:** All data transmitted between the extension and our servers uses HTTPS encryption

### Data Retention
- **Browsing Data:** Stored for 30 days, automatically deleted after
- **Analysis Results:** Retained indefinitely unless you request deletion
- **User Account:** Retained until you uninstall the extension or request deletion

### Security Measures
- Industry-standard encryption (HTTPS/TLS)
- Secure database with row-level security policies
- No sharing of data with third parties (except AI processing)
- Regular security audits and updates

## Third-Party Services

We use the following third-party services:

### OpenAI (ChatGPT)
- **Purpose:** Generate personality insights and productivity analysis
- **Data Shared:** Anonymized summaries of top 15 visited websites (no personal identifiers)
- **Privacy Policy:** https://openai.com/privacy

### Supabase
- **Purpose:** Secure cloud database for storing browsing data and analysis
- **Data Shared:** User UUID, browsing history, analysis results
- **Privacy Policy:** https://supabase.com/privacy

### Render
- **Purpose:** Backend API hosting
- **Data Shared:** API requests and responses
- **Privacy Policy:** https://render.com/privacy

## Your Rights and Choices

### Data Access
You can view all your collected data within the extension's analytics dashboard.

### Data Deletion
To delete your data:
1. Uninstall the Quirk extension from Chrome
2. Your local data will be immediately deleted
3. For cloud data deletion, contact us at: sudhiran541@gmail.com

### Opt-Out
- You can stop data collection at any time by uninstalling the extension
- Disable specific permissions in Chrome extension settings

## Data Sharing

We DO NOT:
- Sell your data to third parties
- Share your personal information with advertisers
- Use your data for marketing purposes
- Share identifiable browsing history publicly

We ONLY share anonymized data summaries with OpenAI for AI analysis.

## Children's Privacy

Quirk is not intended for users under 13 years old. We do not knowingly collect data from children under 13.

## Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted with a new "Last Updated" date. Continued use of Quirk after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.

## Contact Us

If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or want to exercise your data rights:

- **Email:** sudhiran541@gmail.com
- **GitHub:** https://github.com/sudhiraneta/quirk
- **Extension Support:** chrome.google.com/webstore (search for Quirk)

## Compliance

This privacy policy complies with:
- Chrome Web Store Developer Program Policies
- General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR)
- California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA)

## Your Consent

By installing and using Quirk, you consent to this Privacy Policy and our collection and use of data as described.

